parameters: \n<Sawa>\F[90]...Good morning. Huh...? Are we having breakfast now?

\n<Kino>\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Huh? Ah... I was with the director until early
morning, so I just fell asleep like that.

you two so much...

\n<Kino>\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Instead, you'll take care of \N[5]-chan, right? We
wouldn't be able to take care of her so devotedly
like that.

\n<Kino>\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Hehe... Well, don't worry. I left right away, so there's
no need to be concerned. 'There's only a place to
sleep here, after all.'

\n<Kino>\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Mmm, mmm, mmm... Ahh~! Beer in the morning is the best

\n<Sawa>\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[F]Hey... Your elbow is scraped. Don't tell me... Did
something happen with that guy...

\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[F]Kino's right elbow, holding the beer, was red and
swollen, so I couldn't help but associate it with
the marks left by that man.

\n<Kino>\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Ah, no no... This is from yesterday, when I bumped

\n<Kino>\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[FF]It was tough with Momo, you know? They said the

\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[F]......He was at a loss for words. He had been restless
since morning. He couldn't even get a proper meal,
so it wasn't a particularly good state to be in.

\n<Sawa>\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[F](......Is it my fault? Because I did something like that

\n<Kino>\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[FF]...Well, leave that to me, okay? Don't worry about me!

\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Kino, sensing it from seeing the lunch I brought back
for him, showed concern for me in his usual
manner.

\n<Sawa>\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[F](......That's right, it's no good to just lament. I have to do
what I can now...)

\n<Sawa>\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[F]I... I'll go again. At least I want him to have a
proper meal...

\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[F]We looked at each other's faces because we heard a
loud noise coming from the room where he was.

\n<Kino>\F[90]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Did you hear a sound like something big falling just
now...?

\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[F](There's an out-of-place refrigerator in the Western-style
